===Etymology 2===
From {{inh|sh|sla-pro|*kъ(n)}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|sh}} {{m|ine-pro|*kom}}.

====Alternative forms====
* {{l|sh|ка}} (See usage notes)

====Preposition====
{{sh-preposition}}

# [[to]]
# [[towards]]

=====Usage notes=====
Although both {{m|sh|к}} and {{m|sh|ка}} can be used synonymously, {{m|sh|к}} must take the alternative form {{m|sh|ка}} in the following environment:
* before /к, г, х/:
*: ''ка граду'' - to the city
*: ''ка горе'' - towards above
*: ''ка хладу'' - toward the shade

